window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With color, irony, and sensitivity, Pulitzer Prize winner Annie Dillard illuminates the dedication, absurdity, and daring that is the writer’s life. As it probes and exposes, examines and analyzes, <i>The Writing Life</i> offers deeper insight into one of the most mysterious of professions.</p>"; 
